title: There's Nothing You Won't Love About Living At River Trail
posting_body: ['Tucked amid the trees in a private, gated setting, River Trail Apartments offers the inviting atmosphere you crave.', 'You’ll find a refreshing swimming pool, relaxing clubhouse, and playground on our expansive, newly renovated property.', 'Situated near Linden Golf & Country Club in the beautiful Puget Sound region, Puyallup, Washington, offers an ideal setting for work, life, and play.', 'Our pet-friendly one and two bedroom apartments place you near beautiful parks and trails to explore with your pup.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Plank, Wood-Style Flooring', 'Garages Available', 'Walk-In Closets', 'In-Home Washer & Dryer', 'Custom Cabinetry', 'Energy-Efficient Appliances', 'Close to Clarks Creek Park Dog Park', 'Clubhouse with WiFi', 'Private Balcony or Patio', 'Online Rental Payments', 'Dishwasher', 'Playground', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
